            </p>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
  <section id="about" class="flex flex-col">
    <h2
      class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-950 md:text-4xl dark:text-white"
    >
      Sobre Mi
    </h2>
    <article class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-4 md:flex-row">
      <Card className="h-fit text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
          <h3
            class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-950 sm:text-xl dark:text-white"
          >
            Short Bio ðŸ§¬
          </h3>
          <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Iure illo
            distinctio inventore illum consequuntur eveniet nobis officiis sequi
            aspernatur optio nulla, quisquam sit voluptatibus velit cum, minima
            excepturi, numquam explicabo.
          </p>
          <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Enim
            molestias adipisci illum quam eaque perspiciatis saepe rerum
            voluptates cum consectetur? Accusantium reiciendis adipisci error
            corrupti pariatur exercitationem quaerat porro eveniet!
          </p>
          <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Vel animi
            enim rerum perferendis. Distinctio itaque dolores mollitia id, vitae
            necessitatibus earum sed maxime illum sequi impedit nihil. Minus,
            quos non!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <h3
            class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-950 sm:text-xl dark:text-white"
          >
            Informacion CV
          </h3>
          <a
            href="/docs/cv.pdf"
            role="button"
            aria-label="Descargar CV"
            download
            class="w-fit rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-200 focus:outline-hidden dark:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:bg-blue-800 dark:focus:ring-blue-950"
            >Descargar CV</a
          >
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card className="p-8">
        <ol class="relative border-s border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-800">
          {
            EXPERIENCES.map((experience) => (
              <TimelineItem
                title={experience.company}
                description={experience.description}
                date={experience.dates}
              >
                <div
                  slot="icon"
                  class="size-full p-1"
                  set:html={experience.svgIcon}
                />
              </TimelineItem>
            ))
          }
        </ol>
      </Card>
    </article>
  </section>
  <section id="projects" class="flex flex-col">
    <h2
      class="ms-auto mb-8 text-end text-2xl font-bold text-gray-950 md:text-4xl dark:text-white"
    >
      Titulo
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 p-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      {
        PROJECTS.filter((__, i) => i < 3).map((project) => (
          <Project project={project} />
        ))
      }
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
      <a
        role="button"
        href="/projects"
        class="rounded-3xl bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors duration-300 hover:border hover:border-blue-600 hover:bg-transparent hover:text-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-800 dark:hover:border-blue-800 dark:hover:bg-transparent dark:hover:text-blue-800"
        >Ver todos los proyectos</a
      >
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="services" class="flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
    <h2
      class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-950 md:text-4xl dark:text-white"
    >
      Titulo
    </h2>
    <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 p-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      {SERVICES.map((service) => <CardService service={service} />)}
    </article>
  </section>
  <HireServiceModal />
</Layout>

<script>
  import { animate, inView, stagger } from 'motion';

  window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    inView('#services', () => {
      animate(
        '.card-service',
        {
          transform: ['translateY(100%)', 'translateY(0)'],
        },
        {
          delay: stagger(0.2),
          duration: 0.6,
        }
      );
    });

    // AnimaciÃ³n para las tecnologÃ­as
    inView('.tech-stack-card', () => {
      animate(
        '.tech-icon-container',
        {
          opacity: [0, 1],
          transform: ['translateY(30px)', 'translateY(0px)'],
        },
        {
          delay: stagger(0.1),
          duration: 0.5,
        }
      );
    });
  });
</script>
